User Object:
{
  "userId": "String", // A unique identifier for the user, obtained from Auth0
(if we want to send a user confirmation email, can we source their email from Auth0?)
  “email”: “String”, // User’s email address
  "name": "String", // The user's full name
  "phoneNumber": "String", // The user's phone number
  “stripeId”: “String”, // Corresponds to user’s payment details (inc. credit card information) handled by Stripe
  “cartId”: “String” // Identifier of user’s unique shopping cart
  “watchListId”: “String” // Identifier of user’s unique watchlist
  “orderHistory”: “Array” // History of orderIDs for the user
}
